thread.title: William Wiles

author: William Wiles
title: William Wiles
text: I researched self storage online. I found this on on a bing search. Took me to some website, but it wouldn't let me set up a date for an appointment or time. I called the number after a couple days and they sent me an email with a link where I was able to register, rent my unit and pay online. Guess I should have called the number over the weekend.
